## Noncommercial Purposes

Any noncommercial purpose is a permitted purpose.

## Commercial Purposes

Commercial purposes are not permitted purposes.

For purposes of this license, commercial purposes are those
that primarily intend to or are directed toward commercial
advantage or private monetary compensation.  These include
but are not limited to:

1.  selling the software or a copy of the software

2.  selling a good or service that incorporates the software

3.  providing the software as a service

4.  providing a good or service whose value derives primarily
    from the software

